articles.title: Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce Visit Sydney Zoo Following His Arrival in Australia - PEOPLE
articles.description: Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce visited Sydney Zoo on Thursday after the Kansas City Chiefs tight end landed in Australia earlier in the day to support Swift on her Eras Tour.
